      "content": "## Bus route confusion\n- Son’s bus took the wrong route\n- He was about 15 minutes late\n- Driver seemed confused about the run\n\n## Checking and contacting\n- Asked Rachel to monitor the bus\n- Considered calling the bus company\n- Shared the company number: 02920 575333\n\n## Clarifying the problem\n- Route was meant for Bishop / Barry\n- Bus ended up in Penarth\n- One child had said it was the other run\n\n## Situation resolved\n- Company was told about the mistake\n- Bus was redirected and driver knew the route\n- Family agreed to leave it there\n\n## Next steps\n- Keep an eye on the bus\n- Tell Elliot they called\n- No further action needed for now"
